com.clover.sdk.v3.report

Class KeyedSummary

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.clover.sdk.GenericParcelable
      • com.clover.sdk.v3.report.KeyedSummary
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parcelable, JSONifiable, Validator

    public class KeyedSummary
extends GenericParcelable
implements Validator, JSONifiable
    This is an auto-generated Clover data object.

    An object containing all of the fields of a Summary plus one additional key (groupByString). This object is useful for mapping the result set of a SQL query which selects Summaries using a GROUP BY clause.
